259
00:37:35,537 --> 00:37:38,538
So the base height is your buy right.

260
00:37:40,579 --> 00:38:02,477
And then if you want to get those incentive stories, that incentive height, there is a public benefit list that if the developer goes through some of those public benefits, then they could build up to whatever the height, depending on the district.

261
00:38:03,578 --> 00:38:18,052
So this public benefits has attached not a point system but they already tell you how if it's half floor or one floor and if you have those you can get your extra height.

262
00:38:18,632 --> 00:38:19,974
But the base height by right.

263
00:38:22,545 --> 00:38:24,486
your bi-ride height will be the base height.

