00:39:18,034 --> 00:39:27,103
Then we have for the lot area, we have the minimum lot size, lot area will be 3,000, 3,000 for Boston Avenue 1 and 2, and Boston Avenue 3, 5,000.

272
00:39:27,303 --> 00:39:32,728
Frontage, Boston Avenue 1 is 30, Boston Avenue 2 is 40, and Boston Avenue 3 is 40.

273
00:39:32,768 --> 00:39:33,829
Facade buildout, minimum.

274
00:39:40,115 --> 00:39:54,811
Because we have in Boston Avenue 1, we also have the lower intensity for residential, so duplex and triplex, we lowered to 60% the facade buildout.

275
00:39:55,471 --> 00:39:58,194
And then for the other ones, we don't have this.

