So green score, minimum 25, and ideal 30.

285
00:40:45,648 --> 00:40:54,091
And pervious surface is, if they don't do green score, then they have to do the pervious surface, which is 20%, BA1 and 2, and 10% for BA3.

286
00:40:54,231 --> 00:40:58,573
And open landscape minimum is 15%, BA1 and 2, and 10% BA3.

287
00:41:06,072 --> 00:41:14,689
So then for the additional dimensional standards and development standards, it's mainly from Medford Square.

288
00:41:14,829 --> 00:41:17,374
We brought that into Boston Avenue.

