We have a lot of professional young professionals who are trying to you know be able to afford to live here.

335
00:45:53,564 --> 00:45:59,947
And with our housing crunch I think we want people to be able to live together.

336
00:46:00,689 --> 00:46:10,473
if they live together well, but also the idea that we maybe want to discourage lodging houses, which means the landlord is just selecting people and forcing them to live in the same unit together.

337
00:46:10,493 --> 00:46:12,113
