So I don't think that we need a definition for co-living, but I think once you say any five friends who want to live together, suddenly they're a lodging house.

355
00:47:53,075 --> 00:47:54,877
I'm not sure that that was the intent.

356
00:47:55,577 --> 00:47:56,178
Okay.

357
00:47:56,498 --> 00:47:57,459
We can review that one.

358
00:47:57,659 --> 00:47:57,819
Yeah.

