369
00:49:13,808 --> 00:49:20,855
You may or may not like often in a group like that might have a shared meal once a week or something maybe but that would be their choice.

370
00:49:21,451 --> 00:49:34,214
And one of the things we did during the recodification, which predates it, everybody on the council except for Zach and Councillor Behrs and all of the CD board, this, they, sorry.

371
00:49:35,761 --> 00:49:41,886
Councilor Sang was here for the recalcification, thank you, was that we took out the definitions of family.

372
00:49:42,426 --> 00:49:47,009
And I just share this because it has evolved over time.

373
00:49:47,470 --> 00:49:51,533
And when you process that, we're taking out the definition of family and we're saying,

374
00:49:51,933 --> 00:49:53,393
You decide what a family is.

375
00:49:53,814 --> 00:49:55,174
We're not deciding for you.

376
00:49:55,314 --> 00:50:04,357
It literally used to say like husband and wife and children and aunts and uncles, but no further relation than that.

377
00:50:04,397 --> 00:50:08,838
Like it literally spelled that out, which was really problematic.

378
00:50:09,659 --> 00:50:20,022
And what we said was what we really cared about was the crowding, that if this became an unsafe living condition, then the Board of Health would go in as a crowding situation.

379
00:50:20,542 --> 00:50:30,324
And if you have 10 people who are choosing to happily live here and this house is big enough and you're not having crowding issues that trigger the Board of Health, good for you, right?

380
00:50:31,064 --> 00:50:32,204
But how do we do that?

381
00:50:32,244 --> 00:50:34,005
And I think there is actually a choice there.

382
00:50:34,465 --> 00:50:35,225
Do we care?

383
00:50:35,385 --> 00:50:44,447
And we have seen built in the last six years in Medford, houses with five to eight bedrooms, with each bedroom having an attached bathroom.

384
00:50:45,318 --> 00:50:48,119
And they are being separately leased to individuals.

385
00:50:48,619 --> 00:50:51,240
And there was like sort of no way to say that's not allowed.

386
00:50:51,280 --> 00:50:52,421
That's a lodging house.

387
00:50:52,561 --> 00:50:54,242
How does that become a lodging house?

388
00:50:54,422 --> 00:50:54,662
Is it?

389
00:50:55,082 --> 00:51:01,385
And is it therefore actually not allowed under our zoning as opposed to it just being a single family house?

390
00:51:01,905 --> 00:51:03,866
And I think that's, but it's a question.

391
00:51:03,886 --> 00:51:12,109
I did have somebody who was very low income come to me and say, but Alicia, I could afford to live in Medford because I can rent one room in a house like that.

392
00:51:12,449 --> 00:51:15,330
without kitchen privileges, and now I can afford to live here.

393
00:51:15,750 --> 00:51:25,073
