402
00:52:11,537 --> 00:52:16,378
The other thing I do want to raise is that I think there are.

403
00:52:17,298 --> 00:52:29,043
landlords who rent out individual bedrooms and have people who don't know each other living together, and those people may not actually realize that that's what it is because they're renting from afar before coming.

404
00:52:30,160 --> 00:52:41,350
So I think having something, and maybe this is more of a policy that we could pass as a city council, that if you are a lodging house, that you have to disclose that in your application, those kinds of things.

405
00:52:42,011 --> 00:52:47,937
It's not a zoning question, but I think it helps to have a clear definition of lodging house that includes something about

406
00:52:48,477 --> 00:52:56,887
the residents not having this that we removed from the co-living residents have input over the selection of the other residents living in the unit.

407
00:52:56,947 --> 00:53:02,594
