408
00:53:05,204 --> 00:53:11,850
And what I don't know and I think maybe we should look into is what are we allowed to do in terms of regulating leases, right?

409
00:53:12,351 --> 00:53:23,801
Like saying this is a lease, one lease for the whole unit with individual names on it that can get added and removed versus separate leases and people don't see what each other's leases say, right?

410
00:53:23,841 --> 00:53:29,926
So if you have a joint lease with four names on it and four signatures on the bottom, then you all know each other's terms.

411
00:53:30,667 --> 00:53:41,152
And I guess it is possible, right, that he could lease this unit with these terms and that unit with that, those terms, and you don't know the terms the other people have.

412
00:53:41,652 --> 00:53:47,194
